17230.name: MergeText
17230.description:
Merge multiple text layers into one paragraph text.

合并多个文本图层为一个段落文本。


How to use

  1. Select multiple text layers
  2. Run MergeText


如何使用

  1. 选中多个文本图层
  2. 运行 MergeText


Made by Figma.Cool

16965.name: Japanese Brand Colors
16965.description:
Easy to select brand colors in Japan.


日本の企業や店舗のブランドカラーを選択できるプラグインです。

17278.name: Desaturate
17278.description:
Desaturate helps you quickly desaturate one or many layers with image fills. If you work in grayscale and have to manually desaturate images many times a day, this is the plugin for you.


Just select all the layers (with image fills) you want to desaturate and run the plugin. When selecting a frame or a group, it automatically desaturates all children layers as well.


Pro Tip

After running the plugin once, use the "Run Last Plugin" shortcut (⌥⌘P / Alt + Ctrl + P) to run the plugin rapidly.


Desaturate is an open source project. Check it out here.
17278.release_notes: Improved handing of different layer types when desaturating complex frames

17234.name: Bomberos Tracker
17234.description:
Bomberos tracker is a plugin made for managing the activities on the Bomberos Planner community file.


Select a summary card and hit calculate.

17474.name: Soroka
17474.description: Plugin for the selection of font pairs with availability to export an example of using font pair as a template to your artboard

17389.name: Print Resizer
17389.description:
This plugin collects all components from frames in the current figma page and then copies and rearranges them into new printable frames. The printable frames can then be exported and printed on regular letter head. This plugin is especially helpful for frames with auto-layout since they can only scale in only one direction, making printing difficult.


Visit github for more information on how to use the plugin, how to report issues, and how to suggest further improvements.

17442.name: Round to Pixel
17442.description:
Round to remove decimals of attributes such as x, y, width, height, border, and so on


四舍五入，去掉图层 x、y、宽、高、边框、圆角等属性的小数点

17522.name: Screen Name Export
17522.description:
Export selected frame name and link URL to another page in the current file.


  • Get your file URL from share button.
  • Select frames you want to export the name to.
  • Execute this plugin and past your file URL.
  • You will have a new page named "Screen Name ${DateTime}".


More detail is here.
17522.release_notes:
- Let user enter file URL instead of file key for easiness to use.
- Show toast message after the execution.
- Restore file URL from client storage for 30 minutes.

17268.name: Typescale
17268.description: Harmonious typographic scales, directly from your design tool.

17380.name: Similar text selector
17380.description:
Find and select similar text in your designs by font styles. Just choose a text, adapt filter to fit with your preferences, and click on the “Select similar” button.


You can select text similarity by :

  • Same Size
  • Same Weight
  • Same Family


I hope this plugin will help you, as simple as it may be !

17340.name: Export Original Images
17340.description:
This plugin allows you to export images from your selection without any crop and in their native size.


If you ever received a design without the images used in the file attached, this plugin is here to help.


How to use:

  • Select one or multiple elements having an image in their Fill property
  • Run the plugin
  • Save your selection on your computer


Good to know:

  • If you select only one image, the plugin will export that image directly.
  • If you select multiples images, a zip file will be exported.
  • All the images are exported as PNG to avoid losing any information during the export.
  • The original metadata of the images cannot be exported, only the original pixels are.

17290.name: Fast Slice
17290.description:
This plug-in is used by designers to quickly mark the size of the frames(groups) for developers.

  1. Create a slice layer with the same size and the same name in the frame (group).
  2. Prevent developers from selecting elements in the frame, getting the wrong icon size and element position.
  3. Add a red background to mark the size of the frame.

If you find problems or have any suggestions during use, it is recommended to enter the following link to contact me.

https://www.wjx.cn/vj/hmuWich.aspx


设计师可以使用本插件来为开发工程师快速标注切图（支持 frame 和 group）的大小。

  1. 支持在 frame(group) 中创建一个等大、同名的 slice 层。
  2. 支持阻止开发工程师选中 frame(group) 的内部元素，防止他们选中错误的图标、测量到错误的间距。
  3. 支持给 frame 添加半透明的红色背景来标注它的大小。

如果您在使用中发现什么问题或者有一些功能改进的建议，推荐通过下面的链接填写问卷来联系我（使用中文即可）。https://www.wjx.cn/vj/hmuWich.aspx

17199.name: The Write Flavour
17199.description:
Add flavour to your ipsum text with themes like Sport, Fashion, Hard Yakka, Mo Money, Super Luxe, Dining, Cruising and more. 


The paragraphs are compiled from a large collection of selected words and phrases related to each theme. I love Super Luxe and Mo Money myself. 


"...Russian billionaire's bachelor party, Jay Z's guest list skiing in Aspen super yachts private art collection. Upgrade lifestyle Rolls Royce that's B for billions, I'm a Saudi Prince international jetset gold cars in London..."


and Faarshion 

"...Rockin Forever 21 - just turned thirty. What do models eat anyway? Long live the queen - long live Kate Moss, Karl Lagerfeld’s cat Choupette after party Alexander McQueen. I’m Hugo’s boss Burberry trench just another Vogue fashion night out, it’s Prada daahling..."


Want more flavours? Let me know what you want and I'll add them.


Put a smile on your work and a grin on your client's face. 


Note: This is still in Beta. It works nicely, but the sentence compilation still needs a few tweaks.

17424.name: Variant Switcher
17424.description:
The Variant Switcher plugin recursively changes component instances to a different variant based on the specified property.


Usage

The Variant Switcher plugin has three input fields:

  • Property Name: the property you want to change
  • From Variant: (Optional) the current value you want to target (leave blank to select all instances with the selected property regardless of the current value)
  • To Variant: the new value you want to set the property

17357.name: Frame History
17357.description:
The easiest way to save your work and look back at previous iterations. No more manual hassle - get rid of the copy/paste and duplicate files process. 


✅ Save copies of frames you're working on, in a single click.

✅ Explore a visual chronological timeline of your saved frames.

✅ Navigate faster with a time saving version preview.

✅ Easily search and browse through saved frames.


⚙️ How it works

Select the frame you want to save and click the Save button. Frame History will send a copy of the frame to a page called “Frame History” that keeps a visual chronological timeline of your saved versions.


Every time you save a version, Frame History will automatically add a version preview to the plugin’s UI. Version previews are only visible to the creator, and are easy to find using the search feature.


🚀 Roadmap

Frame History is currently in beta. We are planning to add more cool features to make it even better! 


⭐ Help us improve

Got a feature idea? Found a bug? Contact us at ColoRocket.Contact@gmail.com.


📢 License

Enjoy your unlimited Frame History for free (during beta). At the end of the beta period, Frame History will have both free and paid plans.

 

Don’t worry - all the work saved during the beta period will be fully accessible for you, regardless of which plan you choose to go forward with.

17351.name: Print on Demand Automator
17351.description: Do you find yourself spending hours doing repetitive steps just to create print on demand designs? If so, this Figma plugin can give your precious time back. Create a design template with variables. Submit a CSV file. The plugin will replace the variables with the text supplied by your CSV file.
